channel.title: Not here as much
channel.description:
If you haven't noticed, I haven't been all too active like I was before.
Number of reasons.
Jme's pretty much gone, he was my favorite kid on here =/
Not into RS as much. I wasn't before, but now I don't even wanna auto it.
Started a band, and that's occupying(sp) me lots.
I'm in love. Yes I am. She's my life, and I plan to keep it that way.
The only forums I've been recently checking is the music forum.
So if one day I just completely dissapear, here's goodbye and thanks in advance.
Mopar your forums taught me lots and this is the one site I'd recommend to anyone.
